There was a watchful look from BIG CONVOY as he listened to TUSCON,
and although it could not be seen in the darkness a frown was growing
across his face.

&quot;I hear you.&quot; He said finally as TUSCON came to an end. &quot;But you are
heading down a dangerous road.&quot;

CONVOY sat down on a stool and looked over at one of the gratings in
the wall and then back at TUSCON, &quot;Once Magamatron talked much as you
do now. The anger, the desire for vengance. Back when he was one of
the early Maximals.&quot;

